ORG 0       ; Start at Address 0
MVI 5       ; Load loop counter (5) into AC
STA E       ; Store counter in RAM Slot E
MVI 1       ; Load decrement value (1) into AC
STA F       ; Store decrement in RAM Slot F

; --- LOOP START (Address 4) ---
LDA E       ; [Step 1] Load current counter
OUT 1       ; [Step 2] Show counter on Display
SUB F       ; [Step 3] Subtract 1 from counter
STA E       ; [Step 4] Save updated counter to RAM
JNZ 4       ; [Step 5] If AC != 0, Jump back to Address 4

HLT         ; Exit Program